title: Moroccan-inspired lamb kebabs
ingredients: ['1 large onion, roughly chopped', '1 clove garlic, chopped', '6 dried and ready to eat prunes', '500g lamb mince', 'freshly ground pepper', '2 tablespoons breadcrumbs', '1/2 teaspoon ground turmeric', '1/2 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon dried oregano']
